 />\n<br />\n定其實唔可以將佢地諗成同人一樣？ 佢地會唔會覺得定時定候有嘢食，有個安樂窩可以瞓下覺，唔使橫風橫雨出去周街搵嘢食，唔洗擔心搵唔到嘢食咁已經好滿足好幸福？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一諗起呢D野就有D擔心佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"100%明白你諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔使驚, 動物生活好簡單<br />\n<br />\n平時花啲時間陪佢玩, 得閒就摸下佢, 同埋佢嗲你嗰陣陪下佢就得<br />\n<br />\n要俾適合嘅貓糧佢食, 最緊要保持健康<br />\n<br />\n冬天要注意保暖"},{"pid":"3c2339cb7ee5b78a229a706aaaca7f8419353402","tid":1778661,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f89c7e44368f04dd5331e57bdd47987b3e9cb16","tid":1778661,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"另外想問下有冇啲咩玩具係啲貓會自己一個人都會玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買親d咩貓棒，波波個d都要我渣住/我泡先會玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"我有個毛毛波，佢自己踢到癲左，不過成日踢入梳化底要我執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501c3e15d187f6ff52fb4a2031e756fe8739758a","tid":1778661,"uid":204309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"我淨係知狗會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e264d61eab3575984361b5b9288d7a68c05783","tid":1778661,"uid":271171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"咬電線咬鞋大把野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221650a9bb96dda3d084c14ea8889de9197efc17","tid":1778661,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"832c50aa87608c0a389e2c8c199c629e27bd436e","tid":1778661,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d45c1778ba636e575986730c4b4f